71
00:06:38.031 --> 00:06:39.700
(FOOTSTEPS)

72
00:06:40.100 --> 00:06:41.100
(CLICKS)

73
00:06:43.937 --> 00:06:45.372
(EXHALES)

74
00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:50.580
