75
00:06:51.044 --> 00:06:52.179
(SPEAKS IN YAUTJA)

76
00:06:52.279 --> 00:06:53.113
(ELECTRONIC BLIPS)

77
00:06:53.213 --> 00:06:55.248
(WHIRRING)

78
00:06:55.849 --> 00:06:59.250
KWEI: as our ancestors
did before you.

79
00:06:59.750 --> 00:07:03.000
To earn your place in the clan...

80
00:07:03.330 --> 00:07:05.630
...you must choose your prey.

81
00:07:07.130 --> 00:07:09.130
Bring it home...

82
00:07:10.330 --> 00:07:13.000
...or never return.

83
00:07:15.969 --> 00:07:17.437
(WHIRRING)

84
00:07:20.540 --> 00:07:22.420
Wait - Go back!

85
00:07:26.630 --> 00:07:28.170
Genna.

86
00:07:28.540 --> 00:07:30.670
The death planet.

87
00:07:31.880 --> 00:07:35.540
Home of the un-killable Kalisk.

88
00:07:38.759 --> 00:07:41.960
Even father fears it.

89
00:07:43.210 --> 00:07:46.330
Then the Kalisk shall be my trophy.

90
00:07:46.880 --> 00:07:49.460
Father calls me the weakest...

91
00:07:50.420 --> 00:07:53.750
...so I must kill the strongest.

92
00:07:54.710 --> 00:07:57.250
Failure means death.

93
00:07:58.960 --> 00:08:02.000
Then I will not fail.

94
00:08:02.630 --> 00:08:04.790
I cannot allow it.

95
00:08:08.750 --> 00:08:10.420
I make my vow.

96
00:08:10.791 --> 00:08:12.059
(KWEI WHICKERS)

97
00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:15.540
I make my vow!

98
